Keyboard mapping
libinput configuration
Put this in /etc/libinput/local-overrides.quirks: (Source)


[keyd virtual keyboard]
MatchName=keyd virtual keyboard
AttrKeyboardIntegration=internal
ModelTabletModeNoSuspend=1